Enhance CMake configuration and project structure for HesWidgetsDesign
- Updated CMakeLists.txt to improve compiler settings and platform-specific configurations. - Added support for dynamic loading of DWM API functions in HesWinShadowHelper. - Introduced a new CMake configuration file for package management. - Enhanced the example project to automatically create a default main.cpp if no source files are found. - Added build scripts for both Windows (build.bat) and Linux/macOS (build.sh) to streamline the build process. - Improved organization of source files and headers in the project structure. - Implemented installation rules for the library and example project.
feat: 添加 HesWinShadowHelper 类以支持无边框窗口效果和 DWM API 初始化

Add theme management and related resources to HesWidgetsDesign
- Introduced HesTheme class for managing light and dark themes. - Added color macros for consistent theming across the application. - Implemented shadow effects and theme color settings in HesTheme. - Created private implementation for HesTheme to encapsulate theme data. - Added support for Mica display mode in HesApplication. - Included new font (HesAwesome.ttf) and images (Cirno.jpg, MicaBase.png, Moon.jpg, noise.png) for UI enhancements. - Updated CMakeLists.txt to include new source files and dependencies.

feat: Add QtClockWidget and QtEffectWindowManager for enhanced backdrop effects
- Implemented QtClockWidget to display time with various backdrop effects (Acrylic, Blur, Mica, MicaAlt, Aero). - Created QtEffectWindowManager to manage multiple effect windows with grid layout and visibility monitoring. - Introduced QtEffectWindow for robust title bar support, allowing both pure Qt and Win32 implementations. - Unified Qt header management for compatibility across different Qt versions. - Added comprehensive README documentation detailing features, build instructions, usage, and troubleshooting. - Integrated qtacrylicmaterial for optimized background rendering.
